# {{.Name}}

A Docker-based development environment scaffolded by [u-boot](https://github.com/pt9912/u-boot).

## Quickstart

```bash
u-boot up         # start the development stack
u-boot doctor     # check local prerequisites
u-boot down       # stop the stack
```

## Project layout

- `compose.yaml` — Docker Compose stack.
- `docker/` — Dockerfile(s) and container-related assets.
- `scripts/` — project-local helper scripts.
- `docs/` — project documentation.
- `u-boot.yaml` — u-boot project configuration.
- `.env.example` — copy to `.env` and adapt before `u-boot up`.

## Prerequisites

- Docker Engine ≥ 24.0.0
- Docker Compose ≥ 2.20.0
- Git
